originalText.text: Over the last few months, Regina has helped me regain control of my career, specifically to navigate tough conversations, manage complex business objectives, understand myself and my values as a leader, strengthen my team, and skillfully communicate my work up and across my organization.  Our time is always meaningful, I walk away energized, and eager for the next session.  She is an excellent listener, communicator, and thought partner. I can bring any question to her without fear of judgment or feeling like I need to have anything prepared. She is a neutral yet helpful sounding board through which I can think and talk through my toughest work problems. I highly recommend Regina for anybody seeking to improve their leadership performance, create a great team culture, take command of their career growth, and enable their best thinking.

originalText.text: I was amazed at how helpful my sessions with Regina were right from the very beginning. Over the course of a few sessions, she helped me articulate what my goals were and then how to move toward them with a definite and realistic plan. Regina provided that critically informed perspective that enabled me to advocate for myself and move forward to the best opportunity and I couldn't have done it without her help. She is an excellent Leadership Development Coach who offers tremendous value per minute.

originalText.text: After being in Regina’s Mastermind for the past several months, I have grown significantly as a coach.  Regina’s feedback and commitment to her student’s growth helped me take my coaching to the next level.  As the leader, she always brings enthusiasm and positivity while encouraging students to push their edge of development.  Regina is a big proponent of curiosity and experimentation, which is critical in coach development.  I also appreciate and am inspired by Regina’s thirst for feedback and drive to further grow as a master coach and facilitator.  When choosing a facilitator, I had a great feeling about Regina based on her experience and background. I am so pleased I made a great choice!

originalText.text: Regina was incredibly easy to work with, I felt immediately comfortable sharing my challenges and was given tremendous support.   My thoughts were all over the place so it was valuable when she summarized them in a way that made more sense and gave me clarity on the big picture plan for growing my business as well the next steps.  She is so passionate about what she does and I was so motivated by the end of the session.  Thank you Regina for the excellent leadership coaching!

originalText.text: Reflecting on my experience in the Journey to Mastery Coaching Certification program, the most critical experience were the mastermind, practicums, and group coaching sessions facilitated by Executive, Team & Culture coach, Regina Zafonte. In these facilitated settings, Regina established an alliance with us that made our experience safe to be vulnerable, try new things, and consistently work at the edge of our comfort zone.  We connected to what we valued and assembled a toolbox that is now overflowing with resources to improve the experiences we have with our clients. Regina is genuine, easy to connect with, and masterful at supporting growth in others.  Her facilitation and leadership invigorate and inspire continued learning and growing – she more than walks the talk!
